---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Flora Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Flora Endless Word Search by HSL Innovations."
>
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
    <div class="page-app-icon">
        <img
          src="/icons/flora.png"
          alt="Flora app icon"
          class="app-icon"
        />
    </div>
    <h1>Flora Endless Word Search</h1>
    <p>
      Flora is designed with privacy in mind. The app does not display ads,
      track users, or sell personal information.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 2026</p>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 2026</p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Flora Endless Word Search ("Flora") is developed and published by
      HSL Innovations. This Privacy Policy explains what information Flora uses,
      how that information is handled, and how future Apple account features may
      affect the app.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      The current version of Flora does not collect personal information from you.
      Flora does not require you to create an account, provide your name, email
      address, phone number, or location, and does not collect advertising
      identifiers, analytics, or tracking data.
    </p>

    <h2>Game Data</h2>
    <p>
      Flora stores game progress locally on your device so the app can provide
      statistics and gameplay features. This may include information such as:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Puzzles completed</li>
      <li>Words found</li>
      <li>Current streak</li>
      <li>Best streak</li>
      <li>Date you started playing</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      This information stays on your device and is not transmitted to
      HSL Innovations in the current version of the app.
    </p>

    <h2>Apple ID and Future Account Features</h2>
    <p>
      A future version of Flora may support or require Apple account features,
      such as Sign in with Apple, iCloud sync, Game Center, or other Apple
      services. If those features are added, Flora may use your Apple ID only as
      needed to provide the requested app functionality, such as syncing progress
      across devices or associating game progress with your Apple account.
    </p>

    <p>
      HSL Innovations will update this Privacy Policy before any such features
      become available.
    </p>

    <h2>Internet Connection</h2>
    <p>
      The current version of Flora does not require an internet connection to
      play. The app functions offline.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      Flora does not include advertising networks, third-party analytics
      platforms, third-party tracking software, or social media integrations in
      the current version of the app.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      Because the current version of Flora does not collect personal information,
      HSL Innovations does not sell, rent, or share your personal information
      with anyone.
    </p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Flora is designed to be appropriate for players of all ages. The current
      version of the app does not knowingly collect personal information from
      children.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy may be updated as Flora evolves. The effective date at
      the top of this page will indicate the most recent version.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact
      HSL Innovations through the <a href="/support">Support page</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
